To change your e-mail address:
1 - Click on your name located in the bottom right of thinkParity.
2 - Type your new e-mail and press the save button. A verification key will be sent to the new e-mail address and your account will be temporarily placed in an inactive state.
3 - To reactivate your account, click the 'activate your account' link. In the dialog that appears, enter the verification key.